l found it in the lift.

284
00:29:49,000 --> 00:29:51,400
lsn't it yours?
- No... and you know it.

285
00:29:59,000 --> 00:30:01,999
Excuse me! That's mine.
You found it in the lift?

286
00:30:02,000 --> 00:30:03,560
Take it.. 
- Thanks.

287
00:30:08,000 --> 00:30:09,999
Kathamuthu, tell him
l've come to the spot.

288
00:30:10,000 --> 00:30:11,560
No one must stand there.

289
00:30:14,000 --> 00:30:17,000
