Okay, madam.

291
00:30:25,000 --> 00:30:25,960
Hello.

292
00:30:28,000 --> 00:30:29,560
Make it quick please.

293
00:30:38,000 --> 00:30:39,200
Excuse me.

294
00:30:40,000 --> 00:30:42,400
