316
00:31:50,000 --> 00:31:51,800
Asst. Commissioner Anbuselvan.

317
00:31:52,000 --> 00:31:55,000
We solved a land problem together,
in Trustpuram. Do you remember?

318
00:32:01,000 --> 00:32:02,560
What's your name?

319
00:32:04,000 --> 00:32:04,960
Maya

320
00:32:05,000 --> 00:32:08,000
Where's your house?
-No.3, Kasturibai Nagar, Adayar.

321
00:32:11,000 --> 00:32:12,800
You refused to tell me earlier.

322
00:32:16,000 --> 00:32:19,000
Where are you coming from?
- We're coming from watching a movie.

323
00:32:20,000 --> 00:32:20,999
Do you have the tickets?

324
00:32:21,000 --> 00:32:24,600
The tickets had coupons for free juice,
from the Juice Shop on Greams Road.

325
00:32:26,000 --> 00:32:26,999
We used the tickets there.

326
00:32:27,000 --> 00:32:29,999
Who's she? Your sister?
- No sir! We are friends.

327
00:32:30,000 --> 00:32:32,400
Friends means?
- Friends means friends.

328
00:32:35,000 --> 00:32:37,999
Why are you using this road? That's why
we've put barricades here.

329
00:32:38,000 --> 00:32:39,560
Why did you cross them?

330
00:32:42,000 --> 00:32:45,999
You're using it because it is shorter route.
But it's not safe till we set it right again.

331
00:32:46,000 --> 00:32:48,999
And at this time of night,
with a girl by your side...

332
00:32:49,000 --> 00:32:51,400
shouldn't you be carrying all your papers?

333
00:32:52,000 --> 00:32:53,800
Sorry sir.
- Okay, carry on.

334
00:32:55,000 --> 00:32:56,800
Give him the keys.
- Okay sir.

335
00:32:57,000 --> 00:32:58,560
Give him his keys.

336
00:33:05,000 --> 00:33:07,999
l've taken the commissioner's signature.
Don't wait for him.

337
00:33:08,000 --> 00:33:10,999
He's a little busy. You go and present
this file in the Court.

338
00:33:11,000 --> 00:33:13,400
l'll talk to you in the evening.
- Okay sir.

339
00:33:15,000 --> 00:33:16,200
Hello sir.

340
00:33:17,000 --> 00:33:18,800
I met her again
a month later.

341
00:33:23,000 --> 00:33:23,960
Hello!

342
00:33:24,000 --> 00:33:26,400
My name is Maya.
- l know. l remember.

343
00:33:28,000 --> 00:33:30,400
l want to say sorry.
l was a little harsh.

344
00:33:31,000 --> 00:33:34,000
l didn't know then that you
were a police officer.

345
00:33:35,000 --> 00:33:36,999
l understood that from your dirty look.

346
00:33:37,000 --> 00:33:40,000
Did you think l was using the anklet
as a pretext to talk to you?

347
00:33:41,000 --> 00:33:44,000
So, you've realized that police officers
don't roam around with anklets.

348
00:33:45,000 --> 00:33:45,960
Right?

349
00:33:48,000 --> 00:33:50,999
People have a special respect
for the police, don't they?

350
00:33:51,000 --> 00:33:52,800
Good! Go ahead... tell me.

351
00:33:54,000 --> 00:33:56,400
What?
- You said you wanted to apologize.

352
00:33:58,000 --> 00:33:59,999
l'm sorry sir.
l'm really sorry sir.

353
00:34:00,000 --> 00:34:01,800
Your apology is accepted.

354
00:34:02,000 --> 00:34:05,000
lt's good not to talk to strangers...
but don't misjudge people, either.

355
00:34:06,000 --> 00:34:08,400
What are you doing here?
- Sports day!

356
00:34:09,000 --> 00:34:10,560
Student?
- Teacher!

357
00:34:13,000 --> 00:34:15,400
You're a teacher in St. Stephens school...
Maya.

358
00:34:17,000 --> 00:34:20,600
What subjects do you teach? 
- Maths, computer science... 
10th & 12th grade.

359
00:34:22,000 --> 00:34:23,800
Maths for 12th grade - very tough!

360
00:34:25,000 --> 00:34:28,000
What's your qualification?
- MSc. Maths... llT Madras.

361
00:34:31,000 --> 00:34:33,400
llT students can get
good jobs in America.

362
00:34:34,000 --> 00:34:37,000
How come you're a teacher here?
- l like teaching.

363
00:34:43,000 --> 00:34:46,000
l read an article about you,
in last week's Express.

364
00:34:47,000 --> 00:34:48,800
Very impressive sir.
- Thanks.

365
00:34:54,000 --> 00:34:55,999
And l'm sorry...
l'm really sorry.

366
00:34:56,000 --> 00:34:57,800
Don't worry about it, okay?

367
00:35:03,000 --> 00:35:04,560
Bye...
- Bye...

368
00:35:31,000 --> 00:35:33,999
Hello. 
- Anbuselvan sir?
- Speaking, who's this?

369
00:35:34,000 --> 00:35:36,400
Sir, l'm Maya speaking.
Do you remember me?

370
00:35:38,000 --> 00:35:40,400
St. Stephens school.
- Maya... 12th grade maths.

371
00:35:45,000 --> 00:35:47,400
l do remember you...
