have threatened to pour acid on her face.

384
00:36:41,000 --> 00:36:42,999
They followed her to the school
this morning.

385
00:36:43,000 --> 00:36:46,000
She saw them on the bus
and they were here after school also.

386
00:36:47,000 --> 00:36:48,800
What do you think we should do?

387
00:36:49,000 --> 00:36:50,800
Can the police take any action?

388
00:36:51,000 --> 00:36:54,600
Do l have to lodge a formal complaint?
l don't want her to face any problems.

389
00:36:55,000 --> 00:36:58,000
Okay, both of you come with me.
Get into the jeep.

390
00:37:04,000 --> 00:37:05,560
Are they here, Roshini?

391
00:37:06,000 --> 00:37:07,800
They're standing near that auto.

392
00:37:14,000 --> 00:37:15,800
Get down and walk over there.

393
00:37:16,000 --> 00:37:16,960
Sir?

394
00:37:19,000 --> 00:37:20,800
Don't be afraid. l'm here.

395
00:37:21,000 --> 00:37:23,400
Don't let them know l'm here.
Get down & walk.

396
00:37:33,000 --> 00:37:34,999
Hey chickee, think you can slip by silently

397
00:37:35,000 --> 00:37:36,800
if you come home late from school?

398
00:37:37,000 --> 00:37:38,999
Come here. Come over here!
lf you don't come now,

399
00:37:39,000 --> 00:37:41,999
l'll barge into your house and
throw acid on your mother's face.

400
00:37:42,000 --> 00:37:43,200
Get over here!

401
00:37:52,000 --> 00:37:53,999
Come... why are you turning away
when l'm calling you?

402
00:37:54,000 --> 00:37:56,400
Don't you like me?
lsn't my face handsome?

403
00:37:58,000 --> 00:38:00,400
What have you got to lose
by going out with me?

404
00:38:01,000 --> 00:38:02,999
l'm a cool guy.
Why are you making me angry?

405
00:38:03,000 --> 00:38:04,999
Boys, tell her.
- Why are you making him angry?

406
00:38:05,000 --> 00:38:06,999
Didn't he tell you he's a cool guy?

407
00:38:07,000 --> 00:38:09,999
Can't you cut classes & go out with me?
Why are you so reluctant?

408
00:38:10,000 --> 00:38:12,999
Hey. 
- Hey, no need to talk to her.
Pour acid on her face.

409
00:38:13,000 --> 00:38:16,000
Only then she'll understand.
- Come on, give him the acid.

410
00:38:20,000 --> 00:38:22,400
Throw it man.
- No... no... please. No.

411
00:38:26,000 --> 00:38:29,000
Do you know what will happen if l
throw this? Should l do it?

412
00:38:43,000 --> 00:38:44,200
Who's he?

413
00:38:46,000 --> 00:38:46,960
Police!

414
00:38:51,000 --> 00:38:54,000
Sir... sir... we were just joking, sir.
Just like that.

415
00:38:55,000 --> 00:38:57,400
lt isn't acid...
it's just plain water.

416
00:39:00,000 --> 00:39:00,960
Sir..

417
00:39:10,000 --> 00:39:11,800
Just like that.
Just joking.

418
00:39:12,000 --> 00:39:14,400
No bullet. Just an empty pistol.
Got scared?

419
00:39:25,000 --> 00:39:26,800
Come here man!
- l'm a devotee.

420
00:39:28,000 --> 00:39:29,560
Devotee? Go away.

421
00:39:34,000 --> 00:39:34,960
Rogue.

422
00:39:40,000 --> 00:39:40,999
Roshini, go home.

423
00:39:41,000 --> 00:39:42,999
You won't face any more
problems in the future.

424
00:39:43,000 --> 00:39:44,800
Walk bravely down the street.

425
00:39:46,000 --> 00:39:48,400
Remember to walk with
your head held high, okay?

426
00:39:49,000 --> 00:39:49,999
Thank you sir.

427
00:39:50,000 --> 00:39:51,560
l'll get down here.

428
00:39:54,000 --> 00:39:55,560
Are you sure? 
- Yes.

429
00:40:01,000 --> 00:40:04,000
lf it had really been acid?
- My face would have been disfigured.

430
00:40:08,000 --> 00:40:10,400
l can't even think about it.
Thank God!

431
00:40:14,000 --> 00:40:15,200
Thank you.

432
00:40:18,000 --> 00:40:20,999
After that, her face and her eyes used
to haunt me.

433
00:40:21,000 --> 00:40:22,800
Like they were etched in my mind.

434
00:40:23,000 --> 00:40:24,999
I didn't understand
what was happening to me.

435
00:40:25,000 --> 00:40:27,400
I'm couldn't tell if
I liked it or not.

436
00:40:30,000 --> 00:40:31,999
What's this, Anbu? Your punches have
gone soft.

437
00:40:32,000 --> 00:40:33,800
What's happened to you?
-Oh yeah?

438
00:40:34,000 --> 00:40:35,200
Yes.
- Okay.

439
00:40:36,000 --> 00:40:37,800
Okay, eat this.
- Come on...

440
00:40:39,000 --> 00:40:40,200
Let's go.

441
00:40:59,000 --> 00:41:00,560
Hello sir...
- Hello.

442
00:41:02,000 --> 00:41:05,000
l was sitting with a friend in the
coffee shop over there... l saw you.

443
00:41:06,000 --> 00:41:07,800
Would you like to join us?

444
00:41:11,000 --> 00:41:12,560
Sorry, l'm on duty now.

445
00:41:14,000 --> 00:41:16,999
The Chief Minister is coming this way,
l need to be here.

446
00:41:17,000 --> 00:41:18,560
Thanks. You carry on.

447
00:41:19,000 --> 00:41:21,999
So join us after the CM is gone.
We'll wait for you.

448
00:41:22,000 --> 00:41:23,560
Will you join us then?

449
00:41:26,000 --> 00:41:27,999
l'm not sure. l don't know how
much time it'll take.

450
00:41:28,000 --> 00:41:30,400
Don't wait for me.
You carry on, okay?

451
00:41:31,000 --> 00:41:32,560
Okay... bye.
- Bye...

452
00:41:48,000 --> 00:41:51,000
Sir, is that your future wife?
- Mind your own business, Kathamuthu.

453
00:42:38,000 --> 00:42:40,999
Tears which had long forgotten
to drop from my eyes...

454
00:42:41,000 --> 00:42:42,800
fell on her forehead that day.

455
00:42:43,000 --> 00:42:45,400
I had seen many terrible accidents.

456
00:42:46,000 --> 00:42:48,400
Grizzly murders, disgusting scenes...

457
00:42:49,000 --> 00:42:50,800
nothing ever really disturbed me.

458
00:42:51,000 --> 00:42:53,400
But when I saw her badly hurt,
it killed me.

459
00:42:55,000 --> 00:42:57,999
Kathamuthu - her name is Maya.
She's a teacher in St.Stephens.

460
00:42:58,000 --> 00:43:00,999
lnform the school, and tell them
to inform her house also.

461
00:43:01,000 --> 00:43:02,999
Give them my mobile number.
- Okay, sir.

462
00:43:03,000 --> 00:43:04,999
No... no... today is Sunday.
School will be closed.

463
00:43:05,000 --> 00:43:06,999
Call the principal at his
house & inform him.

464
00:43:07,000 --> 00:43:08,999
There's a coffee shop next to the
place we were standing.

465
00:43:09,000 --> 00:43:11,400
She said she had come
there with a friend.

466
00:43:42,000 --> 00:43:45,000
Let's wait for 24 hours, 
l think she should come around 
- Ok doctor.

467
00:44:20,000 --> 00:44:20,960
Hello!

468
00:44:22,000 --> 00:44:23,560
Hello sir. How are you?

469
00:44:26,000 --> 00:44:27,200
How are you?

470
00:44:29,000 --> 00:44:30,560
lt's very painful.

471
00:44:31,000 --> 00:44:32,560
You'll be alright.

472
00:44:34,000 --> 00:44:35,560
l'll get the doctor.

473
00:44:39,000 --> 00:44:41,400
ACP sir...
[Assistant Commissioner of Police]

474
00:44:44,000 --> 00:44:45,800
You missed the CM after all.

475
00:44:47,000 --> 00:44:49,999
lnstead, you were taking me to the
hospital in your car.

476
00:44:50,000 --> 00:44:53,000
Couldn't you have joined me for
a coffee when l invited you?

477
00:44:58,000 --> 00:45:00,400
Why are you so serious?
l was just kidding.

478
00:45:02,000 --> 00:45:05,000
l kept looking at you...
l forgot to look in front of me.

479
00:45:06,000 --> 00:45:09,000
For the first time in our city,
the water tanker won't be accused.

480
00:45:17,000 --> 00:45:19,400
Hello! 
- Hello.
- She's Arthi, Maya's sister.

481
00:45:20,000 --> 00:45:22,400
What happened? How is she now?
- She's okay now.

482
00:45:24,000 --> 00:45:25,999
She was hit by a water tanker
on Mount Road.

483
00:45:26,000 --> 00:45:28,400
She sustained head & limb injuries...

484
00:45:29,000 --> 00:45:31,400
but she'll recover.
You can go in & see her.

485
00:45:32,000 --> 00:45:33,999
*You're spending half your time
*at the hospital.

486
00:45:34,000 --> 00:45:36,400
*l went to see her twice.
*That's all.

487
00:45:41,000 --> 00:45:44,000
But l'm always thinking about her,
